room_title: Escape room "It's All Fun and Games" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: Rumor has it that the Spumonti Toy Shop is a front for some kind of nefarious criminal operation, and it's up to your team to gather the evidence and stop them! Up to 8 detectives can take on this mission at once - can you bust the bad guys?
